                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Base Damage × (1 + Damage Mods) × (1 + Furious Javelin Bonus × (1 + Ability Strength) × #Enemies Hit) = 100 × (1 + 1.2) × (1 + 0.15 × (1 + 0.3) × 5) = 434.5"
